      "content": "but that's just what people say to be nice, isn't it? like... if i actually wasn't here, the space i take up would just be filled by someone else immediately. it's not like i'm leaving a hole. it's more like i was never even in the picture to begin with. it feels more like a relief to just let go of the struggle of trying to be seen.",
